I Hate Horses
[[Image:Princess.jpg|thumb|One of the many horses worthy of your hatred.]]

'''I Hate Horses''' (now know as [http://ifuckinghatehorses.com/ ifuckinghatehorses.com]) is a [[blog]] written by Glue Factory Bob and Dog Food Dale as a means to vent their [[h8|hatred]]. Keep in mind that Glue Factory Bob and Dog Food Dale may be one and the same. And what is it, exactly, that they hate so much? Horses. We're not fucking kidding. Most of their blog is spent stating how much they hate horses, how much they love anything that kills horses, how much they love glue, and how much they hate police for riding horses. Numerous [[pictures plz|pictures]] of horses in embarrassing situations are littered throughout their blog. They also seem to have an affection for [[all caps]].

[[PETA]] (People Eating Tasty Animals) spokesman Spitz agrees with Rachelle:

<blockquote>"''rachelle is right. this isn't funny. horses are the victims of abuse every day. you guys should be ashamed.''"</blockquote>

Both upstanding citizens are wrong. Horse hating is [[funny]] as hell. Almost as fun as sniffing glue, physically participating in the brutal vivisection of a living foal with a blunt Gillette or [[Mr._Hands|getting his ass torn apart by a stallion]].

